{"data":{"contentfulPosts":{"path":"every-step-we-take","category":"songs","body":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"excerpt":"Long we have languished in midnight's monochrome Dreaming of the brilliance that will bloom in theseâ€¦","html":"<p>Long we have languished in midnight's monochrome<br>\nDreaming of the brilliance that will bloom in these shadows<br>\nSo we till the barrenness and scatter seeds of hope<br>\nCome, Lord Jesus in every hand we hold  </p>\n<p>Long we have journeyed o'er marshes, deserts, plains<br>\nYearning for a causeway where children can be safe<br>\nSo we tear down the injustice that keeps our peace in chains<br>\nCome, Lord Jesus in every step we take  </p>\n<p>Sacred light,Come and shine<br>\nHelp us see, Your love grow brighter<br>\nWith every selfless deed  </p>\n<p>Long we have listened to the tune of violence<br>\nLonging for the bright sounds of love to make amends<br>\nSo we don the melody of love's generous strain<br>\nCome, Lord Jesus in every song we sing  </p>\n<p>Come, Lord Jesus in every warm embrace<br>\nCome, Lord Jesus in every stand we take<br>\nCome, Lord Jesus in every smile we bring<br>\nCome, Lord Jesus in every word we speak<br>\nCome, Lord Jesus<br>\nCome, Lord Jesus  </p>"}},"image":{"file":{"url":"//images.ctfassets.net/nvhmztvr2brd/1ke0hpYOvoyCaaWmukUAk8/5dcb1cbf00100d9e96ce579583b5b552/everystep.jpg"},"sizes":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.7777777777777777,"src":"//images.ctfassets.net/nvhmztvr2brd/1ke0hpYOvoyCaaWmukUAk8/5dcb1cbf00100d9e96ce579583b5b552/everystep.jpg?w=1920&q=50","srcSet":"//images.ctfassets.net/nvhmztvr2brd/1ke0hpYOvoyCaaWmukUAk8/5dcb1cbf00100d9e96ce579583b5b552/everystep.jpg?w=480&h=270&q=50 480w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/nvhmztvr2brd/1ke0hpYOvoyCaaWmukUAk8/5dcb1cbf00100d9e96ce579583b5b552/everystep.jpg?w=960&h=540&q=50 960w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/nvhmztvr2brd/1ke0hpYOvoyCaaWmukUAk8/5dcb1cbf00100d9e96ce579583b5b552/everystep.jpg?w=1920&h=1080&q=50 1920w","sizes":"(max-width: 1920px)